== Danish Music Awards ==
The Danish Music Awards is an annual awards ceremony established in 1989 by the Danish department of the [[IFPI]]. Volbeat received four nominations.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=89050 |title=VOLBEAT Nominated In Four Categories At DANISH MUSIC AWARDS  |accessdate=2008-09-02 |publisher=Blabbermouth.net }}</ref>

