== P3 Guld ==
P3 Guld is an annual award ceremony established by the Danish radio station [[DR P3]]. Volbeat have won one award.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.volbeat.dk/pages/bio.html |title=Biography |accessdate=2009-01-07 |publisher=Volbeat }}</ref>

