== Steppeulven ==
The [[Steppeulven]] is an annual award ceremony established by the Association of Danish Music Critics. Volbeat have won one award out of three nominations.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=55211 |title=VOLBEAT Breaks Danish Top 20 |accessdate=2008-09-02 |publisher=Blabbermouth.net }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.steppeulv.dk/nominering2006.htm |title=...og de nominerede 2006 er: |accessdate=2008-09-20 |publisher=steppeulv.dk |language=Danish }}</ref>

